  "texts": [
    "Yet, LLMs embody a neural network approach to AI, applying uniform principles across diverse tasks.",
    "This broad generality might seem excessive.",
    "However, considering LLMs' capability for natural language interaction, their generality is confined to a broad yet specific task.",
    "LLMs can linguistically engage across a vast, indeterminate array of topics, aligning with the level of generality Turing suggested in his discussion on the imitation game.",
    "Moreover, the versatility of LLMs, particularly in more sophisticated versions like OpenAI's GPT-4, extends to multimodality, accepting both image and text inputs, thereby broadening the scope for text generation."
